text: Bannu is a city in Pakistan. Bannu may also refer to: *Bannu District, a district of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan *Bannu Division, an administrative unit of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan *Bannu Airport, an airport in Pakistan *Bannu railway station, a railway station in Pakistan ==See also== *Bannu Biradari, a Hindu community *Bannu Brigade, a former part of India's Northern Command *Bannu Resolution, a resolution from Pashtun community to British Raj in 1947 * * Banu (disambiguation)
title: Bannu (disambiguation)
